       "zip_longest.__class__.__name__.__eq__",
       ["type"],
       true,
       "itertools.zip_longest.__class__.__name__.__eq__('type') == True — zip_longest is a C extension type defined in Modules/itertoolsmodule.c; its metaclass is the built-in type; __class__.__name__ is 'type'; str.__eq__('type') returns True; new to extra135"]
